Pakinggan natin kung ano ang sasabihin ni Ministro Wen.

00:13:09.030 --> 00:13:09.840
Mr. Fan.

00:13:11.390 --> 00:13:13.270
Naaalala ko noong Five-Anti Campaign,

00:13:13.270 --> 00:13:15.070
